column5: Does anyone know where I can get some Skinny Dippers in the Kawartha Lakes area? Thanks, Jimmer Shoot, I realized how that sounds after I posted it. They are a swim bait, not luscious women.
My favorites are the White Trash Skinny Dippers.  But sorry I don't know where you could find them  I know that Paddletale's and Sail in Ottawa has them.
I think the tackle shop in Bridgenorth carries them.
Thanks guys. I'll call Frank in Bridgenorth.
If Bridgenorth doesn't have them, call Ed at Paddletales. He will ship them out to you.
